snippet: Lindsey Vonn failed to finish among the top three in a World Cup super-G for the first time in nearly three years when she was 18th at Bad Kleinkirchheim, Austria, on Sunday.
abstract: American skier Lindsey Vonn fails to finish among the top three in a World Cup super-G for the first time in nearly three years, falling to 18th at Bad Kleinkirchheim, Austria.
lead_paragraph: Lindsey Vonn failed to finish among the top three in a World Cup super-G for the first time in nearly three years when she was 18th at Bad Kleinkirchheim, Austria, on Sunday.

headline.main: Vonn Has Her Worst Super-G in Three Years
